    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-blue);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">1. Sistem Mimarisi</h2>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Veri Akisi</h3>
        <p>Sistem, WebSocket uzerinden gelen canli piyasa verilerini isleyerek sinyal uretir ve trade acar:</p>
        <pre class="docs-code">
  Binance WebSocket
        |
        v
  [CandleWorker]        ← Canli mum verisi alir (5m + 1h)
        |
        v
  [CandleBuffer]        ← Son N mumu bellekte tutar (ring buffer)
        |
        v
  [IndicatorCalculator] ← RSI, MACD, BB, ATR, VWAP, Stochastic, EMA, Volume hesaplar
        |
        v
  [SignalGenerator]     ← 11 adimlik filtre zincirinden gecerek sinyal uretir
        |
        v
  [TradingEngine]       ← PaperBinance veya PaperPoly motoru ile pozisyon acar
        |
        v
  [TradeLogger]         ← SQL Server'a trade kaydeder
        |
        v
  [Dashboard]           ← SignalR ile canli guncelleme
        </pre>

