        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">WebSocket Veri Akisi</h3>
        <p>
            Binance WebSocket API'den <code>kline</code> stream uzerinden 5 dakikalik (5m) ve 1 saatlik (1h) mum verileri alinir.
            Her mum kapandiginda (candle close event) indicator hesaplama ve sinyal uretim sureci tetiklenir.
            1h mumlar sadece trend dogrulama (Adim 5) icin kullanilir, islem acma karari 5m mumlara dayanir.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Bolum 2: Sinyal Skoru Hesaplama -->
    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-green);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">2. Sinyal Skoru Hesaplama</h2>
        <p class="docs-source">Kaynak: <code>TechnicalIndicators.cs:84-136</code></p>

        <p>
            Sinyal skoru, 6 farkli indikatorun agirlikli ortalamasi olarak hesaplanir. Sonuc 0.0 ile 1.0 arasinda bir degerdir.
            0.0 = tam bearish, 1.0 = tam bullish, 0.5 = notr.
        </p>

        <table class="docs-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Bilesen</th>
                    <th>Agirlik</th>
                    <th>Hesaplama</th>
                    <th>Neden Bu Agirlik?</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>RSI(7)</strong></td>
                    <td>%25</td>
                    <td><code>RSI / 100</code> → 0-1 arasi normalize</td>
                    <td>Kisa vadeli momentum en guclu yon gostergesi. 7 periyot hizli tepki verir, scalping icin ideal.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>MACD</strong></td>
                    <td>%20</td>
                    <td>Histogram &gt; 0 ise 1, degilse 0</td>
                    <td>Trend degisimini yakalar. Binary sinyal (bullish/bearish) net karar verir.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Bollinger</strong></td>
                    <td>%20</td>
                    <td><code>(Price - Lower) / (Upper - Lower)</code></td>
                    <td>Fiyatin asiri/eksik degerli oldugunu gosterir. Bant ici pozisyon mean-reversion stratejisi destekler.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>EMA(9)</strong></td>
                    <td>%15</td>
                    <td>Price &gt; EMA → +0.5, EMA rising → +0.5</td>
                    <td>Kisa vadeli trend yonu. Hem fiyat pozisyonu hem momentum (slope) olcer.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Volume</strong></td>
                    <td>%10</td>
                    <td><code>clamp(Ratio / 2, 0, 1)</code></td>
                    <td>Hareketin arkasinda guc var mi? Dusuk hacimli sinyaller guvenilmez. Ratio=2 tam skor verir.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>RSI(14)</strong></td>
                    <td>%10</td>
                    <td><code>RSI / 100</code> → 0-1 arasi normalize</td>
                    <td>Uzun vadeli momentum teyidi. RSI(7) ile tutarliysa sinyal guclu, tutarsizsa zayif.</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Skor Formulu</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
FinalScore = RSI7_norm × 0.25
           + MACD_bull × 0.20
           + BB_position × 0.20
           + EMA9_score × 0.15
           + Volume_norm × 0.10
           + RSI14_norm × 0.10

// Clamp: Math.Clamp(score, 0, 1)
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Fallback Davranisi</h3>
        <p>
            RSI(7) hesaplanamazsa RSI(14) kullanilir. EMA(9) yoksa SMA(10)/SMA(30) karsilastirilir.
            Volume yoksa 0.05 notr deger verilir.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Bolum 3: Filtre Zinciri -->
    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-purple);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">3. 11 Adimlik Filtre Zinciri (V2 Signal Engine)</h2>
        <p class="docs-source">Kaynak: <code>SignalGenerator.cs:216-326</code></p>

        <p>
            Her potansiyel sinyal, asagidaki 11 adimlik filtre zincirinden gecer. Herhangi bir adimda basarisiz olan sinyal reddedilir.
            Bu katmanli yaklasim, dusuk kaliteli trade'leri filtreler.
        </p>

        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">1</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>Minimum Mum Kontrolu</strong>
                <p>En az <code>20</code> mum gereklidir. Yetersiz veriyle sinyal uretilmez.</p>
                <p class="docs-source">Sabit: <code>MinCandlesForSignal = 20</code></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">2</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>Piyasa Fiyat Araligi</strong>
                <p>Market price <code>0.30 - 0.80</code> araliginda olmali. Asiri ucuz veya pahali varliklarda sinyal uretilmez.</p>
                <p class="docs-source">Sabitler: <code>MinMarketPrice = 0.30</code>, <code>MaxMarketPrice = 0.80</code></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">3</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>Agirlikli Skor Hesaplama</strong>
                <p>6 indikatorun agirlikli ortalamasiyla <code>FinalScore</code> hesaplanir (0.0 - 1.0). Detay icin Bolum 2'ye bakin.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">4</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>Yon Karari</strong>
                <p>
                    Skor bazli yon secimi:
                </p>
                <pre class="docs-code">
FinalScore > 0.60 → UP (bullish sinyal)
FinalScore &lt; 0.40 → DOWN (bearish sinyal)
0.40 - 0.60 arasi → REDDEDILIR (yetersiz guven)
                </pre>
                <p>Bu genis notr bant, belirsiz piyasada islem acilmasini onler.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">5</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>1 Saatlik Trend Dogrulama (HARD BLOCK)</strong>
                <p>
                    5 dakikalik sinyal, 1 saatlik trende <strong>ters</strong> ise reddedilir. Bu en kritik filtredir.
                </p>
                <pre class="docs-code">
SMA(5, 1h) ve SMA(10, 1h) hesaplanir:
- SMA_fast > SMA_slow → Hourly trend UP
- SMA_fast &lt; SMA_slow → Hourly trend DOWN

UP sinyal + DOWN trend → REDDEDILIR (counter-trend)
DOWN sinyal + UP trend → REDDEDILIR (counter-trend)
                </pre>
                <p class="docs-source">Kaynak: <code>SignalGenerator.cs:247-263</code></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">6</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>Hacim Dogrulama</strong>
                <p>
                    Hacim orani (mevcut hacim / ortalama hacim) en az <code>0.8</code> olmali.
                    Dusuk hacimli sinyaller guvenilmezdir.
                </p>
                <p class="docs-source">Esik: <code>Volume.Ratio >= 0.8</code></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">7</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>Fair Value Araligi</strong>
                <p>
                    Hesaplanan fair value (FV) da tradeable aralikta olmali: <code>0.30 - 0.80</code>.
                    Asiri degerler reddedilir.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">8</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>UP/DOWN FV Kontrolleri</strong>
                <p>
                    Yonsel ek filtreler:
                </p>
                <pre class="docs-code">
UP sinyal  → FV >= 0.48 zorunlu  (Analyst v2 onerisi)
DOWN sinyal → FV &lt;= 0.52 zorunlu (Analyst v3 onerisi)
                </pre>
                <p>Bu, zayif yonsel sinyallerin filtrelenmesini saglar.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">9</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>Rejim Tespiti (Parkinson Volatility)</strong>
                <p>
                    Piyasa rejimi (dusuk/yuksek volatilite) Parkinson volatilite tahmincisi ile belirlenir:
                </p>
                <pre class="docs-code">
sigma = sqrt(1/(4n*ln2) * SUM(ln(H/L))^2)

volShort = Parkinson(son 12 mum)
volLong  = Parkinson(son 144 mum)

volShort > 1.5 × volLong → HighVolatility
aksi halde               → LowVolatility
                </pre>
                <p>
                    Yuksek volatilite rejiminde minimum edge esigi daha dusuktur (<code>0.12</code>),
                    dusuk volatilitede daha yuksektir (<code>0.15</code>).
                </p>
                <p class="docs-source">Sabitler: <code>RegimeShortPeriod=12</code>, <code>RegimeLongPeriod=144</code>, <code>HighVolMultiplier=1.5</code></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">10</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>Edge Kontrolu (Position Sizing)</strong>
                <p>
                    Kelly Kriteri ile pozisyon buyuklugu hesaplanir. Edge (kenar) minimum esigi asmali:
                </p>
                <pre class="docs-code">
Edge = |FairValue - MarketPrice|

LowVolatility  → MinEdge = 0.15
HighVolatility  → MinEdge = 0.12

Edge &lt; MinEdge → REDDEDILIR
                </pre>
                <p class="docs-source">Kaynak: <code>PositionSizer.cs:8-9</code></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">11</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>Sinyal Olusturma</strong>
                <p>
                    Tum filtrelerden gecen sinyal, SignalScore ile birlikte olusturulur ve ilgili engine'e gonderilir.
                    SignalScore su bilgileri icerir:
                </p>
                <pre class="docs-code">
SignalScore {
    FinalScore,            // agirlikli skor (0-1)
    Edge,                  // |FV - market|
    HourlyTrendConfirmed,  // 1h trend teyidi
    VolumeConfirmed,       // hacim >= 0.8
    IsUpSignal,            // UP yon mu
    IsDownSignal           // DOWN yon mu
}
                </pre>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bolum 4: Pozisyon Boyutlandirma -->
    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-gold);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">4. Pozisyon Boyutlandirma</h2>
        <p class="docs-source">Kaynak: <code>PositionSizer.cs:1-43</code></p>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Kelly Kriteri Formulu</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
// UP pozisyon icin:
kellyFull = (fairValue - marketPrice) / (1 - marketPrice)

// DOWN pozisyon icin:
kellyFull = (marketPrice - fairValue) / marketPrice

// Konservatif carpan:
kellyFraction = kellyFull × 0.15   // %15 Kelly

// Pozisyon buyuklugu:
maxPosition = bankroll × 0.02      // max %2
positionSize = min(kellyFraction × bankroll, maxPosition)
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Neden %15 Konservatif Carpan?</h3>
        <p>
            Tam Kelly (100%) teorik optimum olsa da, pratikte cok agresiftir ve buyuk drawdown'lara yol acar.
            Akademik literaturde genellikle <strong>Half Kelly (%50)</strong> onerilir. Traxon sistemi daha da
            konservatif bir yaklasim benimseyerek <strong>%15 Kelly</strong> kullanir. Bu:
        </p>
        <ul class="docs-list">
            <li>Drawdown'lari minimize eder</li>
            <li>Model hatalarina karsi dayaniklilik saglar</li>
            <li>Uzun vadeli bileşik buyumeyi korur</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Max %2 Pozisyon Limiti</h3>
        <p>
            Her islem bakiyenin en fazla <strong>%2</strong>'si kadar olabilir. 50$'lik bakiye ile bu 1$ demektir.
            Bu kural, tek bir kotu islemin portfoyu ciddi sekilde etkilemesini onler.
        </p>
        <p class="docs-source">Sabit: <code>MaxPositionFraction = 0.02</code></p>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Edge Hesabi</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
Edge = |FairValue - MarketPrice|

// FairValue=0.68, MarketPrice=0.50 → Edge = 0.18 ✓ (> 0.12)
// FairValue=0.55, MarketPrice=0.50 → Edge = 0.05 ✗ (&lt; 0.12, red)
        </pre>
    </div>

    <!-- Bolum 5: PaperBinance Motoru -->
    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-green);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">5. PaperBinance Motoru</h2>
        <p class="docs-source">Kaynak: <code>PaperBinanceEngine.cs:1-351</code></p>

        <p>Binance spot trading simulasyonu. ATR tabanli degil, yuzde tabanli SL/TP kullanir.</p>

        <table class="docs-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Parametre</th>
                    <th>Deger</th>
                    <th>Aciklama</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Stop Loss</strong></td>
                    <td>%0.5</td>
                    <td>Giris fiyatindan %0.5 uzakta. Scalping icin dar SL.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Take Profit</strong></td>
                    <td>%1.0</td>
                    <td>Giris fiyatindan %1.0 uzakta. 1:2 Risk/Odul orani saglar.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Max Hold</strong></td>
                    <td>6 mum</td>
                    <td>6 × 5m = 30 dakika sonra force-close. Uzun bekleyisli zarari onler.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Komisyon</strong></td>
                    <td>%0.075</td>
                    <td>Binance taker fee (BNB ile odendiginde).</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Slippage</strong></td>
                    <td>%0.05</td>
                    <td>Emir kayma simulasyonu.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Min Pozisyon</strong></td>
                    <td>$1</td>
                    <td>Minimum islem buyuklugu.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>TimeFrame</strong></td>
                    <td>5m</td>
                    <td>Sadece 5 dakikalik mumlarda islem acar.</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Neden 1:2 Risk/Odul?</h3>
        <p>
            SL %0.5, TP %1.0 ile her kazanilan islem kaybedilen islemin 2 katini oduyor.
            Bu, <strong>%34</strong> kazanma orani ile bile basabas saglama imkani verir:
        </p>
        <pre class="docs-code">
Basabas WR = SL / (SL + TP) = 0.5 / (0.5 + 1.0) = %33.3

// Yani %34+ win rate ile karli olursunuz!
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">PnL Formulu</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
// UP pozisyon icin:
adjustedExit = exitPrice × (1 - CommissionRate)
entryPrice   = lastCandle.Close × (1 + SlippageRate + CommissionRate)
PnL = (adjustedExit - entryPrice) / entryPrice × positionSize

// DOWN pozisyon icin:
adjustedExit = exitPrice × (1 + CommissionRate)
PnL = (entryPrice - adjustedExit) / entryPrice × positionSize
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">SL/TP Hesaplama</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
// UP pozisyon:
SL = entryPrice × (1 - 0.005)   // %0.5 asagi
TP = entryPrice × (1 + 0.010)   // %1.0 yukari

// DOWN pozisyon:
SL = entryPrice × (1 + 0.005)   // %0.5 yukari
TP = entryPrice × (1 - 0.010)   // %1.0 asagi
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Cikis Mantigi</h3>
        <p>Her mum kapanisinda acik pozisyonlar kontrol edilir:</p>
        <ul class="docs-list">
            <li><strong>TP Hit:</strong> Mumun High (UP) veya Low (DOWN) TP'ye ulasti → kar al</li>
            <li><strong>SL Hit:</strong> Mumun Low (UP) veya High (DOWN) SL'ye ulasti → zarar kes</li>
            <li><strong>MaxHold:</strong> 6 mum (30 dakika) gectiyse → force close (candle.Close'dan)</li>
            <li>Hem TP hem SL ayni mumda hit olursa TP onceliklidir</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Bolum 6: PaperPoly Motoru -->
    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-gold);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">6. PaperPoly Motoru</h2>
        <p class="docs-source">Kaynak: <code>PaperPolymarketEngine.cs:1-276</code></p>

        <p>Polymarket binary-resolution simulasyonu. Kripto fiyat hareketlerini tahmin eden bir tahmin piyasasi motoru.</p>

        <table class="docs-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Parametre</th>
                    <th>Deger</th>
                    <th>Aciklama</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Giris Fiyati</strong></td>
                    <td>0.41 (sabit)</td>
                    <td>0.40 baz fiyat + 0.01 slippage. Dusuk giris = yuksek kazanc asimetrisi.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Komisyon</strong></td>
                    <td>%1.8</td>
                    <td>Taker fee orani.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Min Entry</strong></td>
                    <td>0.25</td>
                    <td>Minimum kabul edilen giris fiyati.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Max Entry</strong></td>
                    <td>0.55</td>
                    <td>Maksimum kabul edilen giris fiyati.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Pozisyon</strong></td>
                    <td>Bakiye × %2</td>
                    <td>Standart Kelly-uyumlu pozisyon buyuklugu.</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Binary Resolution Mantigi</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
// Trade acilir: entryPrice = 0.41 (sabit)

// Mum kapandiginda:
candle.Close >= candle.Open → mum YESIL → UP kazanir
candle.Close &lt;  candle.Open → mum KIRMIZI → DOWN kazanir

// Kazanirsa (resolve = 1.00):
exitPrice = 1.00
fee = positionSize × 0.018
PnL = (1.00 - 0.41) / 0.41 × positionSize - fee
    = +%143.9 × positionSize - fee

// Kaybederse (resolve = 0.00):
exitPrice = 0.00
PnL = -positionSize   // %100 kayip
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Neden Sabit 0.41$ Giris?</h3>
        <p>
            Dusuk giris fiyati, kazanc/kayip asimetrisini maximuma cikarir:
        </p>
        <pre class="docs-code">
Giris: 0.41$
Kazanc: (1.00 - 0.41) / 0.41 = +%143.9
Kayip:  -%100

Basabas hesabi:
  WR × Kazanc = (1 - WR) × Kayip
  WR × 1.439 = (1 - WR) × 1.00
  WR × 1.439 + WR × 1.00 = 1.00
  WR × 2.439 = 1.00
  WR = 1.00 / 2.439 = %41.0

// %41+ kazanma orani → KARLI
// Ornegin %50 WR ile beklenen kar:
//   E[R] = 0.50 × 1.439 - 0.50 × 1.00 = +%22.0 per trade
        </pre>
    </div>

    <!-- Bolum 7: Portfoy Yonetimi -->
    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-red);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">7. Portfoy Yonetimi</h2>
        <p class="docs-source">Kaynak: <code>Portfolio.cs:1-74</code></p>

        <p>
            Her engine bagimsiz bir portfoy yonetir. Portfoy, pozisyon acma/kapama, bakiye takibi ve risk limitleri saglar.
        </p>

        <table class="docs-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Parametre</th>
                    <th>Deger</th>
                    <th>Aciklama</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Baslangic Bakiye</strong></td>
                    <td>$50</td>
                    <td>Her engine 50$ ile baslar.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>MaxExposure</strong></td>
                    <td>Bakiye × %30</td>
                    <td>Ayni anda acik toplam pozisyon bakiyenin %30'unu asamaz.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>MaxPositionSize</strong></td>
                    <td>Bakiye × %2</td>
                    <td>Tek bir pozisyon bakiyenin %2'sini asamaz.</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Pozisyon Acma Akisi</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
1. positionSize > MaxPositionSize → RED
2. TotalExposure + positionSize > MaxExposure → RED
3. Balance &lt; positionSize → RED
4. ONAY: Balance -= positionSize (bakiyeden dusulur)
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Pozisyon Kapama Akisi</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
1. Pozisyonu listeden cikar
2. Balance += positionSize + PnL (geri eklenir)
3. TotalPnL += PnL
4. Win/Loss sayaci guncellenir
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Neden %30 MaxExposure?</h3>
        <p>
            Bakiyenin %70'i her zaman "rezervde" tutulur. Bu:
        </p>
        <ul class="docs-list">
            <li>Ayni anda birden fazla kotu islem olursa bile portfoyu korur</li>
            <li>Yeni firsatlar icin likidite saglar</li>
            <li>En kotu senaryoda (tum acik pozisyonlar %100 kayip) bile bakiyenin %70'i korunur</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Restore Mekanizmasi</h3>
        <p>
            Worker restart sonrasi portfoy durumu SQL Server'daki son snapshot'tan restore edilir.
            Acik pozisyonlar da DB'den yuklenir, boylece SL/TP takibi ve duplicate trade onleme calismaya devam eder.
        </p>
